commit.message: Fixed bug where AI crashes when it gets checked
Fixed bug where AI would make invalid move
Deleted unnecessary folder, double checked that works without
Put all images in an image folder, updated pygame_render.py and gui.py
Updated check_valid_moves.py's pawn function so that the pawn will not be allowed to move two squares on the first move when it is jumping over a piece
switch order of is_in_check in check_checkmate for drastic speed increase
remove redundant conditional statements for boolean returns and remove redundant function inBounds
change parameter name of Col into color and switched order of is_in_check in eval_board_state.py
